         typically with the goal of stealing cargo and other valuable goods. Those who conduct acts of <span><a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Piracy">piracy</a></span> are called pirates,<br>
          while the dedicated ships that pirates use are called pirate ships.</p>
